title: #156: Daddy Dearest (@BrandtTobler)
itunes:title: Daddy Dearest with Brandt Tobler
description: Brandt Tobler and I walked to Runyon Canyon on a hot February afternoon. We talked about what a shitbox father he had. It's a story that has its roots in mall scams that Brandt had worked all through growing up. And it continued to Vegas scams that he ran while living with dear old dad in Sin City.
